    About this hotel

    Set on a bustling main road, this elegant hotel is a 7-minute walk from the museum and plants at Jardin Majorelle, and 8 km from Marrakesh Menara Airport.

    Informal rooms with warm accents include flat-screen TVs, minibars and safes. Suites provide sitting areas.

    Breakfast is available. There's a polished restaurant, and a laid-back cafe/bar with a terrace and city views, as well as a rooftop pool.

    Check-out time: 12:00 PM
